      "span_text": "High pH fractionation with higher flow rates and larger sample amounts is also used to investigate post-translational modifications in great depth by the combination of isobaric mass tag labeling of peptides after digestion, followed by high pH fractionation and consecutive enrichments [CITATION_1] ."
